{"tid":1576492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［集中討論］10月1日·慶國70週年嘅「禮物」","createTime":"2019-09-17T09:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T11:28:10.000Z","uid":17024,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5767811451a6f9ecc5fc8f674176af2599901381","tid":1576492,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"有出面嘅post 話著白衣喪服<br />\n香港人心繫國家，此等盛事又豈能缺席？<br />\n<br />\n本人認為首先要通知國際及本地傳媒<br />\n香港抗爭者喺10月1 呢個普天同慶嘅節日準備咗份大禮畀我地嘅祖國<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n百萬人遊行歌頌偉大祖國（dress code:喪服/白衣）<br />\n煙花時段 18 區燒國旗<br />\n固定時間唱願榮光歸香港<br />\n18區播喪樂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有無咩好主意？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee90e7357e017fa6a250f5bc55807a5fe17a8e3","tid":1576492,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yt2HG33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyt2HG33.jpg&h=9fcb0aae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TrPZKfU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrPZKfU.jpg&h=433e1fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【922攻略流出】<br />\n907<span style=\"color: gold;\">加強版</span>配合hkmap live <br />\n更「大局」交通測試，彩虹戰衣、影帝、機巴、塞鐵、嶄新突擊RB、私家車傾巢而出，裡應外合 <br />\n+機場員工集體Call Sick <br />\n+雷達站/機場附近新搞作<br />\n+大量中港貨櫃司機加入物資支援！<br />\n<br />\n更多攻略，陸續公布，敬請留意"},{"pid":"94d0ed65d33518769293602924affec52f73fe3d","tid":1576492,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"自推10 次<br />\n大家一齊傾傾佢"},{"pid":"658cd077486632dc4cc749dd752fdfd5f37c666c","tid":1576492,"uid":17024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"自推10 次<br />\n大家一齊傾傾佢"},{"pid":"e8885f86d62f523faf6a54b0a397645efb72b657","tid":1576492,"uid":1702